body: Cython compiler generate general PySequence_GetSlice for unicode slice. But unicode objects support own fast execution path for slicing (as substring). This patch allow to generate faster C code for unicode slicing using unicode C-API macroses and C-API functions.

commit.message: Add none check for unicode slicing, remove duplicate code, add test for non-ascii unicode strings and None
Add none check for unicode slicing, remove duplicate code, add test for non-ascii unicode strings and None
Fix test unicode_slicing for compatibility between py2X/py3
Add tests for negative indices in unicode_slicing and PyUnicode_READY in __Pyx_PyUnicode_Substring

title: Add unicode slicing support
